{"id": "1321700842931355689", "channel_id": "1321429949449764975", "type": 0, "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@&1166257943742787615>", "timestamp": "2024-12-26T04:47:16.969000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321429949449764975", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "1？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1321719019480416296", "channel_id": "1321719019480416296", "type": 0, "author_id": "453161298931482626", "author_name": "nightmorals", "author_bot": false, "content": "回坑之後打了一場牌，用的是跟退坑前一樣的ipad mini 6，打的是當初已經打過的羊媽活動，畫面效果全開到最低、只保留60幀，打牌的時候還是瘋狂掉幀，連出牌都卡得不行。\n主畫面也一樣，如果大廳放L2D角色，角色動態也會一卡一卡的。\n半年多前就存在的問題、也很多人回報過，也被承諾會盡快修復，怎麼半年後還是存在呢？", "timestamp": "2024-12-26T05:59:30.596000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-12-26T06:01:28.542000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321719019480416296", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "遊戲卡頓", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1321728202166501406", "channel_id": "1321719019480416296", "type": 0, "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@&1166257943742787615>", "timestamp": "2024-12-26T06:35:59.919000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321719019480416296", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "遊戲卡頓", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1321645979572899912", "channel_id": "1321571433738014741", "type": 0, "author_id": "589115953355423805", "author_name": "magushermes", "author_bot": false, "content": "「想要刷血希祕契」這件事本身不是基礎養成，而是戰術選擇。這不應該是官方引導玩家的。\n而基礎養成，譬如角色經驗值獲取、技能升級材料取得，我覺得官方的引導很清晰了", "timestamp": "2024-12-26T01:09:16.525000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-12-26T01:13:18.068000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321571433738014741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于养成机制的一些小建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1321648962368704513", "channel_id": "1321571433738014741", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156423870379741244", "author_name": "kong760", "author_bot": false, "content": "角色放什麼密契\n在這個遊戲\n基本上是自由的\n沒有米家那種為新角色量身訂製一整套的公式做法\n比如我鯊魚放四月\n有些人會放紅悸\n但老實說開出來的效果\n我覺得我能刷到的四月套優於紅悸\n那我放四月完全沒問題\n不會有太大吃不到某種效果的問題\n個別角色的天賦你也可以在角色頁面觀察要配合什麼詞條加成的密契，我覺得很容易可以看出來\n就這一點如果還要看推薦抄別人密契命輪作業，我會覺得給玩家一種配隊思考上的無形限制", "timestamp": "2024-12-26T01:21:07.679000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321571433738014741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于养成机制的一些小建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1321649223669649429", "channel_id": "1321571433738014741", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156423870379741244", "author_name": "kong760", "author_bot": false, "content": "當然真的不確定放什麼比較好\n這邊的陣容構築版就是讓你放上來討論的", "timestamp": "2024-12-26T01:22:09.978000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321571433738014741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于养成机制的一些小建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1321659410463850590", "channel_id": "1321571433738014741", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "其实玩这个游戏，多看看排行榜，你就会找到大致的答案，然后玩久了你会慢慢产生你自己的理解，就像血希，其实也不是固定的，有人带狼有人带别的，或者你本来不是玩血希的，但是你玩别的角色洗出一套属性很高的密契，比起你没有足够的资源去洗一套小毕业的狼，那或许带别的是更好的选择", "timestamp": "2024-12-26T02:02:38.699000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321571433738014741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于养成机制的一些小建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1321660366840664087", "channel_id": "1321571433738014741", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且这个游戏的属性系统和米差距太大了，米的深渊是没有融灾buff这种东西的，你搭配密契属性的时候还要考虑融灾暴击减半，和深浅又是完全不一样的东西", "timestamp": "2024-12-26T02:06:26.717000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321571433738014741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于养成机制的一些小建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1321681636101984267", "channel_id": "1321571433738014741", "type": 0, "author_id": "725560189981556747", "author_name": "menta_y_menta", "author_bot": false, "content": "雖然我覺得這個系統不錯，但感覺不太適合忘卻🤔忘卻的遊戲方式讓裝備（密契或命輪）的搭配上有很大的靈活度，跟其他遊戲一樣一個角色固定一套畢業裝反而會讓原本的特色消失~~不如裝個該關卡其他玩家的通關隊伍參考~~", "timestamp": "2024-12-26T03:30:57.704000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1321571433738014741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于养成机制的一些小建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
